{"article_id":"3mQ28s2tw5R9ZtqG","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"New York Governor Andrew Cuomo announced an increase in police presence in Jewish communities","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"after an attacker broke into the home of a rabbi in Monsey , New York Saturday night ,","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"stabbing five people .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"Monsey is about 45 miles from New York City .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"The attack follows a string of possibly anti-Semitic crimes","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"that have taken place in New York City since Dec. 13 ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"police say .","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"As of Monday morning , no clear motive had yet been established for the attack .","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"\" A motive now can just be hate , \"","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"said Cuomo ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"speaking in a television interview .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"\" Hate is the new currency in this country...","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"at our worst , we fear differences ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"we demonize differences","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"and that is what we are seeing over this past year , two years all across the country .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"It ' s in the political world ,","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"but it has gone viral . \"","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"Some Jewish neighborhoods of New York City will see an increase in police presence in response to a string of recent attacks ,","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"Mayor Bill de Blasio announced Friday .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"Police will be deployed to the Borough Park , Crown Heights and Williamsburg neighborhoods of Brooklyn","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"and there will be an increase in police visits to houses of worship and \" other critical areas in the community , \"","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"de Blasio said in a Friday tweet .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"Police did not immediately say","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"how many officers would be deployed to the neighborhoods .","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"\" Hate doesn ' t have a home in our city , \"","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"he wrote .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"\" Anyone","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"who terrorizes our Jewish community","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"WILL face justice . \"","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"Police are investigating several possible anti-Semitic attacks","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"that have occurred throughout New York City in recent weeks ,","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"the New York Police Department","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"( NYPD )","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"told reporters at a press conference Friday .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"Investigations include one attack","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"that took place on Friday morning","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"in which three Jewish women were slapped in the face by another woman","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"who , during interrogation , told police","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"she committed the crime","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"because she thought","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"the three women were Jewish .","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"Cuomo announced","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"the State Police hate crimes task force would help NYPD in investigations","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"following three other attacks","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"that happened on Dec. 24 , after the start of the Hanukkah holiday ,","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"including two men","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"who were struck","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"while walking down a street .","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"State police and the NYPD are also currently assisting the Ramapo Police Department in the investigation of the stabbing in Monsey ,","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"Cuomo said Sunday morning .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"\" This is terrorism ,","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"it is domestic terrorism \"","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"Cuomo said at a Sunday morning press conference at the Ramapo Police Department .","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"\" These are people","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"who intend to create mass harm , mass violence ,","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"generate fear","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"based on race , color , creed","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"- that is the definition of terrorism . \"","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"Get The Brief .","depth":3},{"id":59,"text":"Sign up","depth":4},{"id":60,"text":"to receive the top stories","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"you need to know right now .","depth":5},{"id":62,"text":"Choose your country","depth":5},{"id":63,"text":"United States of America","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"Afghanistan Albania Algeria American Samoa Andorra","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"Angola Anguilla Antigua and Barbuda Argentina Armenia Aruba Australia Austria Azerbaijan Bahamas Bahrain Bangladesh Barbados Belarus Belgium Belize Benin Bermuda Bhutan Bolivia","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"Bosnia and Herzegovina Botswana Brazil Brunei Darussalam Bulgaria Burkina Faso Burundi Cambodia Cameroon Canada","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"Cape Verde Cayman Islands","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"Central African Republic","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"Chad Chile China Colombia Comoros","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"Congo Congo , Democratic Republic of Cook Islands","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"Costa Rica Cote d'Ivoire","depth":15},{"id":72,"text":"Croatia Cuba","depth":16},{"id":73,"text":"Cyprus Czech Republic Denmark Djibouti Dominica Dominican Republic","depth":18},{"id":74,"text":"Ecuador Egypt El Salvador Equatorial Guinea Eritrea Estonia Ethiopia","depth":18},{"id":75,"text":"Faeroe Islands","depth":17},{"id":76,"text":"Falkland Islands","depth":18},{"id":77,"text":"( Malvinas )","depth":18},{"id":78,"text":"Fiji Finland France French Guiana French Polynesia","depth":18},{"id":79,"text":"Gabon Gambia Georgia Germany Ghana Gibraltar Greece Greenland Grenada Guadeloupe Guam Guatemala Guinea Guinea-Bissau Guyana Haiti Holy See Honduras Hong Kong Hung